<br>
This is preferable to the weeks-long camp, but does bring up other problems.  Every low-end named mob in Skyfire is snagged by a dr00d within minutes of spawning.  15 clerics and their friends squabbling over two dozen mobs seems like more headache than 6 clerics waiting in line for one mob...<br>
<br>
but then, I got my epic before the Ragefire change.  72 hours.  Camped it in 16-hour stretches with my roommate to spell me for 6 hours or so of sleep.  It was miserable and dehumanizing and stupid for a game, but that's the lengths we're willing to take to get the epic.<br>
<br>
And don't suffer disrespect to our system.  Our system works.  The Rathe is a mature server for the most part.  If you want to go play with the kiddies, there are plenty of other places for you to go.  Consider the Rathe to be the retirement community of EQ.<br>
